"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلرَّحِيمُ","translation":"পরম দয়ালু\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_098_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70776,"position":10,"arabic":"٩٨","translation":"(৯৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":99,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا دَخَلُوا۟ عَلَىٰ يُوسُفَ ءَاوَىٰٓ إِلَيْهِ أَبَوَيْهِ وَقَالَ ٱدْخُلُوا۟ مِصْرَ إِن شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ ءَامِنِينَ","translation":"AND WHEN they [all arrived in Egypt and] presented themselves before Joseph, he drew his parents unto himself, saying, \"Enter Egypt! If God so wills, you shall be secure [from all evil]!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1695.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":70849,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70850,"position":2,"arabic":"دَخَلُوا۟","translation":"তারা উপস্থিত হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70851,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"নিকট","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70852,"position":4,"arabic":"يُوسُفَ","translation":"ইউসুফের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70853,"position":5,"arabic":"ءَاوَىٰٓ","translation":"সে জায়গা দিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70854,"position":6,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِ","translation":"তার কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70855,"position":7,"arabic":"أَبَوَيْهِ","translation":"তার পিতা-মাতাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70856,"position":8,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","translation":"এবং সে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70857,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱدْخُلُوا۟","translation":"\"আপনারা প্রবেশ করুন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70858,"position":10,"arabic":"مِصْرَ","translation":"মিশরে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70859,"position":11,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70860,"position":12,"arabic":"شَآءَ","translation":"চান","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70861,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70862,"position":14,"arabic":"ءَامِنِينَ","translation":"নিরাপদ (থাকবেন)\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_099_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70863,"position":15,"arabic":"٩٩","translation":"(৯৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":100,"arabic":"وَرَفَعَ أَبَوَيْهِ عَلَى ٱلْعَرْشِ وَخَرُّوا۟ لَهُۥ سُجَّدًۭا ۖ وَقَالَ يَٰٓأَبَتِ هَٰذَا تَأْوِيلُ رُءْيَٰىَ مِن قَبْلُ قَدْ جَعَلَهَا رَبِّى حَقًّۭا ۖ وَقَدْ أَحْسَنَ بِىٓ إِذْ أَخْرَجَنِى مِنَ ٱلسِّجْنِ وَجَآءَ بِكُم مِّنَ ٱلْبَدْوِ مِنۢ بَعْدِ أَن نَّزَغَ ٱلشَّيْطَٰنُ بَيْنِى وَبَيْنَ إِخْوَتِىٓ ۚ إِنَّ رَبِّى لَطِيفٌۭ لِّمَا يَشَآءُ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ هُوَ ٱلْعَلِيمُ ٱلْحَكِيمُ","translation":"And he raised his parents to the highest place of honour; and they [all] fell down before Him, prostrating themselves in adoration. Thereupon [Joseph] said: \"O my father! This is the real meaning of my dream of long ago, which my Sustainer has made come true. And He was indeed good to me when He freed me from the prison, and [when] He brought you [all unto me] from the desert after Satan had sown discord between me and my brothers. Verily, my Sustainer is unfathomable in [the way He brings about] whatever He wills: verily, He alone is all-knowing, truly wise!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1696.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":71312,"position":1,"arabic":"وَرَفَعَ","translation":"এবং চড়ালেন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_100_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71313,"position":2,"arabic":"أَبَوَيْهِ","translation":"তার পিতা-মাতাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_100_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":71314,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/012_100_003.mp3","c